'orthodox'>{}"},"kv17.4:4.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv17.4:4.3":{"pli":"Nanu yadaniccaṁ taṁ dukkhaṁ vuttaṁ bhagavatā—","html":"{}"},"kv17.4:4.4":{"pli":"“anindriyabaddhaṁ aniccan”ti? ","html":"{}"},"kv17.4:4.5":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv17.4:4.6":{"pli":"Hañci yadaniccaṁ taṁ dukkhaṁ vuttaṁ bhagavatā—","html":"{}"},"kv17.4:4.7":{"pli":"“anindriyabaddhaṁ aniccaṁ”, no ca vata re vattabbe—","html":"{}"},"kv17.4:4.8":{"pli":"“indriyabaddhaññeva dukkhan”ti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv17.4:5.1":{"pli":"Na vattabbaṁ—","html":"<p data-doxy='heterodox'>{}"},"kv17.4:5.2":{"pli":"“indriyabaddhaññeva dukkhan”ti? ","html":"{}"},"kv17.4:5.3":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv17.4:5.4":{"pli":"Yathā indriyabaddhassa dukkhassa pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṁ vussati, evamevaṁ anindriyabaddhassa dukkhassa pariññāya bhagavati brahmacariyaṁ vussatīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv17.4:5.5":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv17.4:5.6":{"pli":"yathā indriyabaddhaṁ dukkhaṁ pariññātaṁ na puna uppajjati, evamevaṁ anindriyabaddhaṁ dukkhaṁ pariññātaṁ na puna uppajjatīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv17.4:5.7":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe. ","html":"{}"},"kv17.4:5.8":{"pli":"Tena hi indriyabaddhaññeva dukkhanti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv17.4:5.9":{"pli":"Indriyabaddhakathā niṭṭhitā. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"kv17.5":{"kv17.5:0.1":{"pli":"Kathāvatthu ","html":"<article id='kv17.5'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"kv17.5:0.2":{"pli":"Mahāpaṇṇāsaka ","html":"<li>{}</li>"},"kv17.5:0.3":{"pli":"Sattarasamavagga ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"kv17.5:0.4":{"pli":"Ṭhapetvāariyamaggantikathā ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"kv17.5:1.1":{"pli":"Ṭhapetvā ariyamaggaṁ avasesā saṅkhārā dukkhāti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv17.5:1.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv17.5:1.3":{"pli":"Dukkhasamudayopi dukkhoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv17.5:1.4":{"pli":"Na hevaṁ vattabbe …pe… ","html":"{}"},"kv17.5:1.5":{"pli":"dukkhasamudayopi dukkhoti? ","html"