ceva pūjito bhavissāmi saṅgho cā”ti. ","html":"{}"},"kv17.9:3.6":{"pli":"Attheva suttantoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv17.9:3.7":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv17.9:3.8":{"pli":"Tena hi saṅghassa dinnaṁ mahapphalanti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv17.9:4.1":{"pli":"Na vattabbaṁ—","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv17.9:4.2":{"pli":"“saṅghassa dinnaṁ mahapphalan”ti? ","html":"{}"},"kv17.9:4.3":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv17.9:4.4":{"pli":"Nanu sakko devānamindo bhagavantaṁ etadavoca—","html":"{}</p>"},"kv17.9:5.1":{"pli":"“Yajamānānaṁ manussānaṁ, ","html":"<blockquote class='gatha'><p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:5.2":{"pli":"puññapekkhāna pāṇinaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:5.3":{"pli":"Karotaṁ opadhikaṁ puññaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:5.4":{"pli":"kattha dinnaṁ mahapphalan”ti. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"kv17.9:6.1":{"pli":"“Cattāro ca paṭipannā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:6.2":{"pli":"cattāro ca phale ṭhitā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:6.3":{"pli":"Esa saṅgho ujubhūto, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:6.4":{"pli":"paññāsīlasamāhito. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"kv17.9:7.1":{"pli":"Yajamānānaṁ manussānaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:7.2":{"pli":"puññapekkhāna pāṇinaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:7.3":{"pli":"Karotaṁ opadhikaṁ puññaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:7.4":{"pli":"saṅghe dinnaṁ mahapphalanti. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"kv17.9:8.1":{"pli":"Eso hi saṅgho vipulo mahaggato, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:8.2":{"pli":"Esappameyyo udadhīva sāgaro; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:8.3":{"pli":"Ete hi seṭṭhā naravīrasāvakā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:8.4":{"pli":"Pabhaṅkarā dhammamudīrayanti. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"kv17.9:9.1":{"pli":"Tesaṁ sudinnaṁ suhutaṁ suyiṭṭhaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:9.2":{"pli":"Ye saṅghamuddissa dadanti dānaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:9.3":{"pli":"Sā dakkhiṇā saṅghagatā patiṭṭhitā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:9.4":{"pli":"Mahapphalā lokavidūna vaṇṇitā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"kv17.9:10.1":{"pli":"Etādisaṁ yaññamanussarantā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:10.2":{"pli":"Ye vedajātā vicaranti loke; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:10.3":{"pli":"Vineyya maccheramalaṁ samūlaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"kv17.9:10.4":{"pli":"Aninditā saggamupenti ṭhānan”ti. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>"},"kv17.9:11.1":{"pli":"Attheva suttantoti? ","html":"<p>{}"},"kv17.9:11.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv17.9:11.3":{"pli":"Tena hi saṅghassa dinnaṁ mahapphalanti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv17.9:11.4":{"pli":"Na vattabbaṁ saṅghassa dinnaṁ mahapphalantikathā niṭṭhitā. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"kv18.1":{"kv18.1:0.1":{"pli":"Kathāvatthu ","html":"<article id='kv18.1'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"kv18.1:0.2":{"pli":"Niggahapaṇṇāsaka ","html":"<li>{}</li>"},"kv18.1:0.3":{"pli":"Aṭṭhārasamavagga ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"},"kv18.1:0.4":{"pli":"Manussalokakathā ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"kv18.1:1.1":{"pli":"Na vattabbaṁ—","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv18.1:1.2":{"pli":"“buddho bhagavā manussaloke aṭṭhāsī”ti? ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:1.3":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:1.4":{"pli":"Nanu atthi buddhavutthāni cetiyāni ārāmavihāragāmanigamanagarāni raṭṭhāni janapadānīti? ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:1.5":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:1.6":{"pli":"Hañci atthi buddhavutthāni cetiyāni ārāmavihāragāmanigamanagarāni raṭṭhāni janapadāni, tena vata re vattabbe—","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:1.7":{"pli":"“buddho bhagavā manussaloke aṭṭhāsī”ti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv18.1:2.1":{"pli":"Na vattabbaṁ—","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv18.1:2.2":{"pli":"“buddho bhagavā manussaloke aṭṭhāsī”ti? ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:2.3":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:2.4":{"pli":"Nanu bhagavā lumbiniyā jāto, bodhiyā mūle abhisambuddho, bārāṇasiyaṁ bhagavatā dhammacakkaṁ pavattitaṁ, cāpāle cetiye āyusaṅkhāro ossaṭṭho, kusinārāyaṁ bhagavā parinibbutoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:2.5":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:2.6":{"pli":"Hañci bhagavā lumbiniyā jāto …pe… kusinārāyaṁ bhagavā parinibbuto, tena vata re vattabbe—","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:2.7":{"pli":"“buddho bhagavā manussaloke aṭṭhāsī”ti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv18.1:3.1":{"pli":"Na vattabbaṁ—","html":"<p data-doxy='orthodox'>{}"},"kv18.1:3.2":{"pli":"“buddho bhagavā manussaloke aṭṭhāsī”ti? ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:3.3":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:3.4":{"pli":"Nanu vuttaṁ bhagavatā—","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:3.5":{"pli":"“ekamidāhaṁ, bhikkhave, samayaṁ ukkaṭṭhāyaṁ viharāmi subhagavane sālarājamūle”ti; ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:3.6":{"pli":"“ekamidāhaṁ, bhikkhave, samayaṁ uruvelāyaṁ viharāmi ajapālanigrodhe paṭhamābhisambuddho”ti; ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:3.7":{"pli":"“ekamidāhaṁ, bhikkhave, samayaṁ rājagahe viharāmi veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe”ti; ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:3.8":{"pli":"“ekamidāhaṁ, bhikkhave, samayaṁ sāvatthiyaṁ viharāmi jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme”ti; ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:3.9":{"pli":"“ekamidāhaṁ, bhikkhave, samayaṁ vesāliyaṁ viharāmi mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyan”ti. ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:3.10":{"pli":"Attheva suttantoti? ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:3.11":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:3.12":{"pli":"Tena hi buddho bhagavā manussaloke aṭṭhāsīti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv18.1:4.1":{"pli":"Buddho bhagavā manussaloke aṭṭhāsīti? ","html":"<p data-doxy='heterodox'>{}"},"kv18.1:4.2":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:4.3":{"pli":"Nanu bhagavā loke jāto, loke saṁvaḍḍho, lokaṁ abhibhuyya viharati anupalitto lokenāti? ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:4.4":{"pli":"Āmantā. ","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:4.5":{"pli":"Hañci bhagavā loke jāto, loke saṁvaḍḍho, lokaṁ abhibhuyya viharati anupalitto lokena, no ca vata re vattabbe—","html":"{}"},"kv18.1:4.6":{"pli":"“buddho bhagavā manussaloke aṭṭhāsī”ti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"kv18.1:4.7":{"pli":"Manussalokakathā niṭṭhitā. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}}}